title: Kate Siegel
itunes:title: Kate Siegel
description:
On a wildly surreal episode of GFY, Whitney's high school “nemesis” and now Hollywood Horror Queen Kate Siegel (Netflix’s Haunting of Hill House, The Haunting of Bly Manor, Midnight Mass) reunite after twenty-two years and heal some major wounds, gossip about making it in Hollywood, and compare notes on being pitted against each other by a teacher in high school, who they now realize “groomed” them. Trigger warning?
